LYRICS

Talk talk talk, and it’s breaking my heart 
(And) all you do is talk talk talk talk (X2) 

You think  that I can’t read your game, oh oh 
But I can beat ya poker face, any day any day 
You’re all talk, all ^words, (but) lem me tell ya what I heard 
You’re always spinning ^stories 
Oh I got your number down, oh oh 
No need  to put one over but you’re so proud so proud 
Ya all talk, sound blurbs, don’t  believe a single word 
Is that all you got for me 

Blah blah blah are the words that you’re say^ing 
I didn’t wanna know but now I know I can’t go back 
Blah blah blah is the sound that I’m hearing
Blah, blah blah blah 

All you do is, Talk, Talk, Talk, Talk (ehh ehh)
Running on your mouth and thinkin’ I’m not onto you
All you do is, Talk Talk Talk Talk (ehh ehh)
Stop wasting’ all my time, ^yeah, with your stupid lines
 I don’t need no other, reason no not to bother
It’s only that you’re never tell the truth boy,
all you do is talk, talk, talk, talk
talk talk talk, and it’s breaking my heart 

Hey boy
いつも君はデマカセばかり
お得意の嘘on嘘のはなし
時間の問題
終わりしか見えない愛
残念だけどもう？
‘’Baby I don’t need you.‘’
いい加減にしてよ Ma boo 
マジで変わらない態度に Uh...
何回言っても変わんない
意地の張り合い
もう散々よ
マジでないわ

Blah blah blah 
聞き飽きた　fake game 
知りたいよ　けど傷つきたくない
Blah blah blah Sayonara to your name 
Blah, blah blah blah 

All you do is, Talk, Talk, Talk, Talk (ehh ehh)
Running on your mouth and thinkin’ I’m not onto you
Talk, Talk, Talk, Talk (ehh ehh)
言い訳ばかりBoy  これで終わりね
 I don’t need no other, reason no not to bother
It’s only that you’re never tell the truth boy,
all you do is talk, talk, talk, talk
talk talk talk, and it’s breaking my heart 

Oh Oh これ以上は
I want you off my mind 
Oh Oh 本当は君の言葉聞きたいの

How ‘bout ya : shut it, shut it up, shut it up, shut it up (X3) 
Blah, blah blah blah 

All you do is, Talk, Talk, Talk, Talk (ehh ehh)
Running on your mouth and thinkin’ I’m not onto you
All you do is, Talk Talk Talk Talk (ehh ehh)
Stop wasting’ all my time, ^yeah, with your stupid lines
 I don’t need no other, reason no not to bother
It’s only that you’re never tell the truth boy,
all you do is talk, talk, talk, talk
talk talk talk, and it’s breaking my heart 

Runnin it up runnin it up, your mouth Talk Talk Talk... 

All you do is, Talk Talk Talk Talk (ehh ehh)
Stop wasting’ all my time, yeah, with your stupid lines I don’t need no other, reason no not to bother
It’s only that you’re never tell the truth boy,
all you do is talk, talk, talk, talk
talk talk talk, and it’s breaking my heart 

RAP Can’t listen to you run your mouth, everyone else gatherin’ round and let me help you break it down - ooooh
Everytime I hear you speak, it's like a game of hide and seek
always lies, never truth — tell you whatcha ought to do 

BRIDGE 
Ohh  Ohh, No I don’t wanna hear it I want - you - off my mind 
Ohh  Ohh, No ^I don’t really need this, I need ^someone to believe ^in 
*How ‘bout ya : shut it, shut it up, shut it up, shut it up (X3) 
Blah Blah Blah Blah, Blah* 

OUTRO
